S.FORM: aicu ti Kuo Hsing Chun (ciniukukan: inamizukuan:Tana) mavan a unduin nase nua aya. nalemedaw kemasi imaza i yilan king. timadju kemasi imaza i taitu i valangaw a qinaljan uta. na kitjuala kemasi i na pakata undu kaucung a gaku kitjeljc sihu taitu daigaku katua nase tinsiukiu kuzing a vuren daigaku itua undu a tatuluan. avan sika tucu namasan tua huciawsu imaza i vuren daigaku se undu a tatuluan. timadju namalap tua liawliaw a pazangal a tjaljavavavan a pakaleva nase paqaqayam a , parutua ka 2020 a caviljan aulingpiya undukai imaza i ripun i tukiyu, na kialap tua sangasangasan a pakaleva pakata nase vavayan a 59 a kinasadjelung katua mareka paqaqayam imaza i kacauan. ka 2017 a caviljan timajdu na paselaw tjaljavavavan a tinsu izua 142 a kinasadjelung itua , namsan ta sangasangasan a tinsu se vavayan a unduin i kacauan tuazua. ka tjaivililj ta 2018 a caviljan patje tucu timadju mavananga tjaljasangasangasan a unduin nasevavayan namalap tua vavavan a tinsu pakata 59 a kinasadjelung itua , , katua penuljat a tinsu matja tjelu a i kacauan. kipalikuzan pakaleva
